data.description: Modern concept; NO HOA; private gate; pool with beautiful water features, tanning ledge, and hot tub; outdoor kitchen and living space with fireplace...CHOOSE KELLER OR SOUTHLAKE ISD! Oversized windows offer ample natural light in this incredible open concept layout that warm and welcoming. This stunning home boasts high end finishes and exquisite details throughout with the extras you have been dreaming of! Stunning Chef's Kitchen includes Thermador appliances, 6 burners and double oven, gorgeous quartz countertops, TWO butlers panties connected by oversized walkthrough pantry. Custom laundry suite with ample cabinets and a PET SHOWER! Master suite is the perfect escape with a spa-like bathroom and stackable washer dryer combo in the amazing closet! First floor also offers your perfect home office and game room. Oak Hardwood floors throughout the first floor! Impressive modern staircase, custom light fixtures. Energy-efficient with Generac backup! OVERSIZED THREE CAR GARAGE!!
